c: 40
v: 64
t: "Allah ni Ajula jwantendele litaka kuŵa lyakutamilichika, liwunde nikuŵa nsakasa, ni ampaanjiile kaoneche kenu, basi ni akakolosyisye kaoneche kenuko, ni ampele ichindu yambone, Jwalakwe ni Allah M’mbuje gwenu, basi anyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Allah, M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"